docs/perturbseq-qc_2026-07-07\pyzobot_referee_batch.py:14:chain_score combines the four hops on comparable log/normalized scales:
docs/perturbseq-qc_2026-07-07\pyzobot_referee_batch.py:15:    kd_term       weight the whole chain by gate pass (0/1; candidates are all 1)
